<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <prefix>§</prefix>
  <num>18-904</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Choice of law regarding execution.</heading>
  <para>
    <num undesignated="true">(a)</num>
    <text>A will executed electronically but not in compliance with <cite path="§18-905|(a)">§ 18-905(a)</cite> is an electronic will under <cite path="18|9">this chapter</cite> if executed in compliance with the law of the jurisdiction where the testator is:</text>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text>Physically located when the will is signed; or</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text>Domiciled or resides when the will is signed or when the testator dies.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
